<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2902] List of collations are wrong parsed in SpellCheckResponse</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2902</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I do a search query which &lt;tt&gt;spellcheck=on&lt;/tt&gt; I get more then one collation in the solr response:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;kaart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;maart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;vaart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;staart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;baart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;komkaart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&quot;collation&quot;&amp;gt;dagvaart&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SpellCheckResponse gives me only the collation &apos;dagvaart&apos;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;getCollatedResults()&lt;/tt&gt; gives a list of 7 items that contains only Collation objects with &apos;dagvaart&apos;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;getCollatedResult()&lt;/tt&gt; gives a string with the value &apos;dagvaart&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;windows xp.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
